title: DMSO treated MDA-MB231 exosomes (24 h treatment)_rep1
source_name_ch1: Exosomes from DMSO treated MDA-MB231 (24 h treatment)_rep1
characteristics_ch1.2: disease state: adenocarcinoma/derived from metastatic site
treatment_protocol_ch1: Cells were treated 100渭M of SFX for 24 hours under serum-free condition.
growth_protocol_ch1: MDA-MB231 cells were grown under following condition: Dulbecco Modified Eagle Medium (DMEM) with 10 % fetal bovine serum (FBS) and 1% antibiotic and antimycotic agent.
extract_protocol_ch1: Exosomes were isolated by Exoquick reagent (SBI). Total RNA was extracted using Total exosome RNA and protein isolation kit. Experiment was performed according to the manufacturer's instruction
label_protocol_ch1: RNA was labeled using Affymetrix® FlashTag™ Biotin HSR RNA Labeling Kit
hyb_protocol: Labeled targets were hybridized to the Affymetrix miRNA 4.0 chip, GeneChips were washed and stained in the Affymetrix Fluidics Station 450
scan_protocol: Raw data were extracted automatically in Affymetrix data extraction protocol using the software provided by Affymetrix GeneChip庐 Command Console庐 Software (AGCC).
description: miRNA gene expression data of exosomes derived from DMSO (vehicle)-treated MDA-MB231
data_processing: The CEL files import, miRNA level RMA+DABG-All analysis and result export using Affymetrix庐 Power Tools (APT) Software.
